summary: Woke up at 7, went for a run, then studied Android at the library by 9. Worked on SAM project. Felt exhausted and low motivation but still followed the daily structure, which prevented guilt of wasting time. Despite working hard, felt results were insufficient. At night, watched Eternal Sunshine of the Spotless Mind and cried while processing grief about past relationship with Tanvi. The emotional release reduced bitterness and cleared the head, leaving a sense of acceptance.

wins: Studied Android and worked on SAM consistently
Processed grief and reduced bitterness towards past relationship
losses: Felt inefficient and insufficient despite hard work
ideas: Daily structure is working as a stabilizer even when motivation is low

goals: Use reflection to manage emotional challenges
triggerEvents: Crying while watching Eternal Sunshine of the Spotless Mind
